Package: libdaybo-config-reader-perl
Architecture: all
Provides: dl-libconfreader-perl
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, perl, liberror-perl
Description: Code for quickly reading configuration files from Perl scripts
 Due to a wide range of fairly broken modules on CPAN which don't keep options
 within their sections, 2E0EOL wrote this handle little package for easily
 reading configuration in a few number of lines.
